              "free_text": [
                " Cross-section",
                "measurements were made by comparing the yield of the",
                "9.7 MeV gamma ray from the 10B(p,gamma)11C reaction",
                "with that of the 6.14 MeV gamma ray from the",
                "19F(p,alpha+gamma) 16O reaction at the 1.348 MeV",
                "resonance using the same geometry. This was taken as",
                "89 mb from the work of Chao et al. The cross sections",
                "for the lower energy gamma rays were then estimated",
                "by comparison with the yield of the 9.7 MeV gamma ray,",
                "with appropriate allowances being made for changes in",
                "the detection geometry and variation in crystal",
                "sensitivity. The uncertainty in the result is",
                "estimated to be about 50%.)"
              ]
            }
          ],
